{
  "video_id": "ONM4JupBz_E",
  "title": "Robert Neuwirth: The power of the informal economy",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15965.0,
      "end_time": 18190.0,
      "text": "In System D, this"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18190.0,
      "end_time": 20237.0,
      "text": "is a store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20237.0,
      "end_time": 22564.0,
      "text": "and what I mean by that is that this is a photograph"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22564.0,
      "end_time": 27879.0,
      "text": "I took in Makoko, shantytown in Lagos, Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27879.0,
      "end_time": 30262.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s built over the lagoon, and there are no streets"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30262.0,
      "end_time": 32780.0,
      "text": "where there can be stores to shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32780.0,
      "end_time": 33968.0,
      "text": "and so the store comes to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33968.0,
      "end_time": 35753.0,
      "text": "And in the same community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35753.0,
      "end_time": 37505.0,
      "text": "this is business synergy."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37505.0,
      "end_time": 41611.0,
      "text": "This is the boat that that lady was paddling around in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41611.0,
      "end_time": 44351.0,
      "text": "and this artisan makes the boat and the paddles"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44351.0,
      "end_time": 45656.0,
      "text": "and sells directly"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45656.0,
      "end_time": 47820.0,
      "text": "to the people who need the boat and the paddles."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47820.0,
      "end_time": 50200.0,
      "text": "And this is a global business."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50200.0,
      "end_time": 54128.0,
      "text": "Ogandiro smokes fish in Makoko in Lagos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54128.0,
      "end_time": 57890.0,
      "text": "and I asked her, \"Where does the fish come from?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57890.0,
      "end_time": 59815.0,
      "text": "And I thought she&#39;d say, \"Oh, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59815.0,
      "end_time": 62715.0,
      "text": "up the lagoon somewhere, or maybe across Africa,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62716.0,
      "end_time": 64147.0,
      "text": "but you&#39;ll be happy to know she said"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64147.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66204.0,
      "text": "it came from here, it comes from the North Sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66204.0,
      "end_time": 68529.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s caught here, frozen, shipped down to Lagos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68530.0,
      "end_time": 71617.0,
      "text": "smoked, and sold for a tiny increment of profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71617.0,
      "end_time": 73139.0,
      "text": "on the streets of Lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73139.0,
      "end_time": 74990.0,
      "text": "And this is a business incubator."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74990.0,
      "end_time": 78692.0,
      "text": "This is Olusosun dump, the largest garbage dump in Lagos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78692.0,
      "end_time": 81762.0,
      "text": "and 2,000 people work here, and I found this out"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81763.0,
      "end_time": 84181.0,
      "text": "from this fellow, Andrew Saboru."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84181.0,
      "end_time": 88341.0,
      "text": "Andrew spent 16 years scavenging materials on the dump,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88341.0,
      "end_time": 91568.0,
      "text": "earned enough money to turn himself into a contract scaler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91569.0,
      "end_time": 94179.0,
      "text": "which meant he carried a scale and went around and"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94179.0,
      "end_time": 96403.0,
      "text": "weighed all the materials that people had scavenged"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96403.0,
      "end_time": 99426.0,
      "text": "from the dump. Now he&#39;s a scrap dealer."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99426.0,
      "end_time": 101827.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s his little depot behind him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101827.0,
      "end_time": 106338.0,
      "text": "and he earns twice the Nigerian minimum wage."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106338.0,
      "end_time": 108600.0,
      "text": "This is a shopping mall."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108600.0,
      "end_time": 110774.0,
      "text": "This is Oshodi Market in Lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110775.0,
      "end_time": 113121.0,
      "text": "Jorge Luis Borges had a story called \"The Aleph,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113121.0,
      "end_time": 114943.0,
      "text": "and the Aleph is a point in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114944.0,
      "end_time": 117239.0,
      "text": "where absolutely everything exists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117239.0,
      "end_time": 119584.0,
      "text": "and for me, this image is a point in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119584.0,
      "end_time": 122480.0,
      "text": "where absolutely everything exists."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122480.0,
      "end_time": 124897.0,
      "text": "So, what am I talking about when I talk about System D?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124897.0,
      "end_time": 127196.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s traditionally called the informal economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127196.0,
      "end_time": 130824.0,
      "text": "the underground economy, the black market."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130824.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133117.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t conceive of it that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133117.0,
      "end_time": 135874.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s really important to understand that something like"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135874.0,
      "end_time": 140353.0,
      "text": "this is totally open. It&#39;s right there for you to find."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140354.0,
      "end_time": 143810.0,
      "text": "All of this is happening openly, and aboveboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143810.0,
      "end_time": 145602.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nothing underground about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 145603.0,
      "end_time": 148985.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s our prejudgment that it&#39;s underground."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 148985.0,
      "end_time": 153490.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve pirated the term System D from the former French colonies."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153490.0,
      "end_time": 156586.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a word in French that is d√©brouillardise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156586.0,
      "end_time": 158706.0,
      "text": "that means to be self-reliant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158706.0,
      "end_time": 162690.0,
      "text": "and the former French colonies have turned that into"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 162690.0,
      "end_time": 164625.0,
      "text": "System D for the economy of self-reliance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164626.0,
      "end_time": 167884.0,
      "text": "or the DIY economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167884.0,
      "end_time": 171120.0,
      "text": "But governments hate the DIY economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 171130.0,
      "end_time": 174257.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why -- I took this picture in 2007,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174257.0,
      "end_time": 178809.0,
      "text": "and this is the same market in 2009 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178809.0,
      "end_time": 181115.0,
      "text": "and I think, when the organizers of this conference"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181115.0,
      "end_time": 182542.0,
      "text": "were talking about radical openness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 182542.0,
      "end_time": 185980.0,
      "text": "they didn&#39;t mean that the streets should be open"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185980.0,
      "end_time": 186841.0,
      "text": "and the people should be gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 186841.0,
      "end_time": 190784.0,
      "text": "I think what we have is a pickle problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 190784.0,
      "end_time": 193724.0,
      "text": "I had a friend who worked at a pickle factory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193724.0,
      "end_time": 195625.0,
      "text": "and the cucumbers would come flying down"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195625.0,
      "end_time": 199628.0,
      "text": "this conveyer belt, and his job was to pick off the ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199628.0,
      "end_time": 201976.0,
      "text": "that didn&#39;t look so good and throw them in the bin"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 201977.0,
      "end_time": 203883.0,
      "text": "labeled \"relish\" where they&#39;d be crushed and mixed"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203883.0,
      "end_time": 207209.0,
      "text": "with vinegar and used for other kinds of profit."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207209.0,
      "end_time": 209520.0,
      "text": "This is the pickle economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 209520.0,
      "end_time": 212250.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all focusing on ‚Äî this is a statistic from"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 212250.0,
      "end_time": 214604.0,
      "text": "earlier this month in the Financial Times ‚Äî"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214604.0,
      "end_time": 218147.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re all focusing on the luxury economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 218147.0,
      "end_time": 220890.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s worth 1.5 trillion dollars every year, and that&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 220890.0,
      "end_time": 222634.0,
      "text": "a vast amount of money, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 222634.0,
      "end_time": 225881.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s three times the Gross Domestic Product of Switzerland."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 225882.0,
      "end_time": 230680.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s vast. But it should come with an asterisk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 230680.0,
      "end_time": 234873.0,
      "text": "and the asterisk is that it excludes two thirds of the workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 234873.0,
      "end_time": 235926.0,
      "text": "of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 235926.0,
      "end_time": 239315.0,
      "text": "1.8 billion people around the world work"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 239315.0,
      "end_time": 244851.0,
      "text": "in the economy that is unregulated and informal."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 244851.0,
      "end_time": 248131.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a huge number, and what does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248131.0,
      "end_time": 252884.0,
      "text": "Well, it means if it were united in a single political system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 252884.0,
      "end_time": 257139.0,
      "text": "one country, call it"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 257139.0,
      "end_time": 260140.0,
      "text": "\"The United Street Sellers Republic,\" the U.S.S.R.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260140.0,
      "end_time": 261973.0,
      "text": "or \"Bazaaristan,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 261973.0,
      "end_time": 266249.0,
      "text": "it would be worth 10 trillion dollars every year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 266249.0,
      "end_time": 268305.0,
      "text": "and that would make it the second largest economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268305.0,
      "end_time": 270786.0,
      "text": "in the world, after the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 270786.0,
      "end_time": 273626.0,
      "text": "And given that projections are that the bulk"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 273626.0,
      "end_time": 277291.0,
      "text": "of economic growth over the next 15 years will come"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 277291.0,
      "end_time": 280663.0,
      "text": "from emerging economies in the developing world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 280663.0,
      "end_time": 282794.0,
      "text": "it could easily overtake the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 282794.0,
      "end_time": 286159.0,
      "text": "and become the largest economy in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 286160.0,
      "end_time": 289695.0,
      "text": "So the implications of that are vast, because it means"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 289695.0,
      "end_time": 293218.0,
      "text": "that this is where employment is ‚Äî 1.8 billion people ‚Äî"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 293218.0,
      "end_time": 297840.0,
      "text": "and this is where we can create a more egalitarian world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297840.0,
      "end_time": 301811.0,
      "text": "because people are actually able to earn money and live"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 301811.0,
      "end_time": 304806.0,
      "text": "and thrive, as Andrew Saboru did."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 304806.0,
      "end_time": 306967.0,
      "text": "Big businesses have recognized this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 306967.0,
      "end_time": 308945.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s fascinating about this slide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 308946.0,
      "end_time": 311204.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not that the guys can carry boxes on their heads"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 311204.0,
      "end_time": 313719.0,
      "text": "and run around without dropping them off."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 313719.0,
      "end_time": 316814.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s that the Gala sausage roll is a product that&#39;s made"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 316814.0,
      "end_time": 319524.0,
      "text": "by a global company called UAC foods"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 319524.0,
      "end_time": 322910.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s active throughout Africa and the Middle East,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 322910.0,
      "end_time": 325780.0,
      "text": "but the Gala sausage roll is not sold in stores."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 325780.0,
      "end_time": 329116.0,
      "text": "UAC foods has recognized that it won&#39;t sell if it&#39;s in stores."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 329117.0,
      "end_time": 333222.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s only sold by a phalanx of street hawkers"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 333222.0,
      "end_time": 336340.0,
      "text": "who run around the streets of Lagos at bus stations"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 336350.0,
      "end_time": 340508.0,
      "text": "and in traffic jams and sell it as a snack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 340508.0,
      "end_time": 343530.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s been sold that way for 40 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 343530.0,
      "end_time": 345700.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a business plan for a corporation."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 345700.0,
      "end_time": 348193.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 348193.0,
      "end_time": 351306.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s Mr. Clean looking amorously at all the other"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 351306.0,
      "end_time": 353226.0,
      "text": "Procter & Gamble products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 353226.0,
      "end_time": 355674.0,
      "text": "and Procter & Gamble, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 355674.0,
      "end_time": 358251.0,
      "text": "the statistic always cited is that Wal-Mart"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 358251.0,
      "end_time": 363920.0,
      "text": "is their largest customer, and it&#39;s true, as one store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 363107.0,
      "end_time": 366294.0,
      "text": "Wal-Mart buys 15 percent, thus 15 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 366294.0,
      "end_time": 369394.0,
      "text": "of Procter & Gamble&#39;s business is with Wal-Mart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 369394.0,
      "end_time": 372955.0,
      "text": "but their largest market segment is something that they call"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 372955.0,
      "end_time": 375875.0,
      "text": "\"high frequency stores,\" which is all these tiny kiosks"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 375875.0,
      "end_time": 379186.0,
      "text": "and the lady in the canoe and all these other businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 379186.0,
      "end_time": 384532.0,
      "text": "that exist in System D, the informal economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 384533.0,
      "end_time": 387931.0,
      "text": "and Procter & Gamble makes 20 percent of its money"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 387931.0,
      "end_time": 389979.0,
      "text": "from that market segment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 389980.0,
      "end_time": 393416.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the only market segment that&#39;s growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 393416.0,
      "end_time": 396524.0,
      "text": "So Procter & Gamble says, \"We don&#39;t care whether a store"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 396524.0,
      "end_time": 399418.0,
      "text": "is incorporated or registered or anything like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 399418.0,
      "end_time": 403251.0,
      "text": "We want our products in that store.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 403251.0,
      "end_time": 405423.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s mobile phones."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 405423.0,
      "end_time": 407263.0,
      "text": "This is an ad for MTN,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 407263.0,
      "end_time": 409905.0,
      "text": "which is a South African multinational"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 409905.0,
      "end_time": 412654.0,
      "text": "active in about 25 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 412654.0,
      "end_time": 414215.0,
      "text": "and when they came into Nigeria ‚Äî"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 414215.0,
      "end_time": 416171.0,
      "text": "Nigeria is the big dog in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 416172.0,
      "end_time": 418496.0,
      "text": "One in seven Africans is a Nigerian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 418496.0,
      "end_time": 421198.0,
      "text": "and so everyone wants in to the mobile phone market"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 421198.0,
      "end_time": 423232.0,
      "text": "in Nigeria. And when MTN came in, they wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 423232.0,
      "end_time": 426192.0,
      "text": "to sell the mobile service like I get in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 426192.0,
      "end_time": 429966.0,
      "text": "or like people get here in the U.K. or in Europe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 429966.0,
      "end_time": 433855.0,
      "text": "expensive monthly plans, you get a phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 433855.0,
      "end_time": 435855.0,
      "text": "you pay overages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 435855.0,
      "end_time": 437983.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re killed with fees --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 437983.0,
      "end_time": 439787.0,
      "text": "and their plan crashed and burned."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 439787.0,
      "end_time": 441827.0,
      "text": "And they went back to the drawing board, and they retooled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 441827.0,
      "end_time": 443331.0,
      "text": "and they came up with another plan:"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 443331.0,
      "end_time": 445517.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t sell you the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 445517.0,
      "end_time": 447347.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t sell you the monthly plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 447347.0,
      "end_time": 450483.0,
      "text": "We only sell you airtime."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 450483.0,
      "end_time": 452396.0,
      "text": "And where&#39;s the airtime sold?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 452396.0,
      "end_time": 456489.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s sold at umbrella stands all over the streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 456489.0,
      "end_time": 460212.0,
      "text": "where people are unregistered, unlicensed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 460213.0,
      "end_time": 462918.0,
      "text": "but MTN makes most of its profits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 462918.0,
      "end_time": 465605.0,
      "text": "perhaps 90 percent of its profits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 465605.0,
      "end_time": 470267.0,
      "text": "from selling through System D, the informal economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 470267.0,
      "end_time": 472103.0,
      "text": "And where do the phones come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 472103.0,
      "end_time": 474977.0,
      "text": "Well, they come from here. This is in Guangzhou, China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 474977.0,
      "end_time": 478412.0,
      "text": "and if you go upstairs in this rather sleepy looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 478413.0,
      "end_time": 483390.0,
      "text": "electronics mall, you find the Guangzhou Dashatou"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 483390.0,
      "end_time": 485912.0,
      "text": "second-hand trade center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 485912.0,
      "end_time": 489960.0,
      "text": "and if you go in there, you follow the guys with the muscles"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 489960.0,
      "end_time": 491758.0,
      "text": "who are carrying the boxes, and where are they going?"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 491758.0,
      "end_time": 494575.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to Eddy in Lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 494575.0,
      "end_time": 497279.0,
      "text": "Now, most of the phones there are not second-hand at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 497279.0,
      "end_time": 498586.0,
      "text": "The name is a misnomer."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 498586.0,
      "end_time": 501494.0,
      "text": "Most of them are pirated. They have the name brand"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 501494.0,
      "end_time": 504575.0,
      "text": "on them, but they&#39;re not manufactured by the name brand."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 504575.0,
      "end_time": 507231.0,
      "text": "Now, are there downsides to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 507231.0,
      "end_time": 510479.0,
      "text": "Well, I guess. You know, China has no ‚Äî"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 510479.0,
      "end_time": 513770.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) ‚Äî no intellectual property, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 513770.0,
      "end_time": 515671.0,
      "text": "Versace without the vowels."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 515672.0,
      "end_time": 517734.0,
      "text": "Zhuomani instead of Armani."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 517734.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522741.00000000006,
      "text": "S. Guuuci, and -- (Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 522741.0,
      "end_time": 525870.0,
      "text": "All around the world this is how products"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 525870.0,
      "end_time": 528390.0,
      "text": "are being distributed, so, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 528390.0,
      "end_time": 531549.0,
      "text": "in one street market on Rua 25 de Mar√ßo"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 531549.0,
      "end_time": 533518.0,
      "text": "in S√£o Paulo, Brazil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 533518.0,
      "end_time": 536814.0,
      "text": "you can buy fake designer glasses."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 536814.0,
      "end_time": 538877.0,
      "text": "You can buy cloned cologne."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 538877.0,
      "end_time": 541651.0,
      "text": "You can buy pirated DVDs, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 541652.0,
      "end_time": 544509.0,
      "text": "You can buy New York Yankees caps"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 544509.0,
      "end_time": 547715.0,
      "text": "in all sorts of unauthorized patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 547715.0,
      "end_time": 550804.0,
      "text": "You can buy cuecas baratas, designer underwear"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 550804.0,
      "end_time": 553101.0,
      "text": "that isn&#39;t really manufactured by a designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 553101.0,
      "end_time": 557475.0,
      "text": "and even pirated evangelical mixtapes. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 557475.0,
      "end_time": 560229.0,
      "text": "Now, businesses tend to complain about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 560229.0,
      "end_time": 563768.0,
      "text": "and their, they, I don&#39;t want to take away from their"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 563768.0,
      "end_time": 565806.0,
      "text": "entire validity of complaining about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 565806.0,
      "end_time": 570304.0,
      "text": "but I did ask a major sneaker manufacturer earlier this year"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 570304.0,
      "end_time": 573201.0,
      "text": "what they thought about piracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 573201.0,
      "end_time": 574548.0,
      "text": "and they told me, \"Well, you can&#39;t quote me on this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 574548.0,
      "end_time": 576648.0,
      "text": "because if you quote me on this, I have to kill you,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 576648.0,
      "end_time": 582352.0,
      "text": "but they use piracy as market research."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 582352.0,
      "end_time": 585576.0,
      "text": "The sneaker manufacturer told me that if"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 585576.0,
      "end_time": 589263.0,
      "text": "they find that Pumas are being pirated, or Adidas"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 589263.0,
      "end_time": 592549.0,
      "text": "are being pirated and their sneakers aren&#39;t being pirated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 592549.0,
      "end_time": 595434.0,
      "text": "they know they&#39;ve done something wrong. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 595434.0,
      "end_time": 598511.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s very important to them to track piracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 598511.0,
      "end_time": 600875.0,
      "text": "exactly because of this, and the people who are buying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 600875.0,
      "end_time": 602995.0,
      "text": "the pirates, are not their customers anyway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 602995.0,
      "end_time": 605727.0,
      "text": "because their customers want the real deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 605727.0,
      "end_time": 607220.0,
      "text": "Now, there&#39;s another problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 607220.0,
      "end_time": 610552.0,
      "text": "This is a real street sign in Lagos, Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 610552.0,
      "end_time": 613616.0,
      "text": "All of System D really doesn&#39;t pay taxes, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 613616.0,
      "end_time": 615420.0,
      "text": "And when I think about that, first of all I think that"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 615421.0,
      "end_time": 619135.0,
      "text": "government is a social contract between the people and"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 619135.0,
      "end_time": 621651.0,
      "text": "the government, and if the government isn&#39;t transparent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 621651.0,
      "end_time": 623872.0,
      "text": "then the people aren&#39;t going to be transparent either,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 623872.0,
      "end_time": 626920.0,
      "text": "but also that we&#39;re blaming the little guy"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 626920.0,
      "end_time": 628857.0,
      "text": "who doesn&#39;t pay his taxes, and we&#39;re not recognizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 628857.0,
      "end_time": 631630.0,
      "text": "that everyone&#39;s fudging things all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 631630.0,
      "end_time": 635663.0,
      "text": "including some extremely respected businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 635663.0,
      "end_time": 636803.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll give you one example."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 636803.0,
      "end_time": 640954.0,
      "text": "There was one company that paid 4,000 bribes"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 640954.0,
      "end_time": 643352.0,
      "text": "in the first decade of this millennium, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 643352.0,
      "end_time": 648252.0,
      "text": "a million dollars in bribes every business day, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 648253.0,
      "end_time": 650548.0,
      "text": "All over the world. And that company"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 650548.0,
      "end_time": 653454.0,
      "text": "was the big German electronics giant Siemens."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 653454.0,
      "end_time": 657332.0,
      "text": "So this goes on in the formal economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 657332.0,
      "end_time": 659530.0,
      "text": "as well as the informal economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 659530.0,
      "end_time": 661660.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s wrong of us to blame ‚Äî and I&#39;m not singling out"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 661660.0,
      "end_time": 665379.0,
      "text": "Siemens, I&#39;m saying everyone does it. Okay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 665379.0,
      "end_time": 668828.0,
      "text": "I just want to end by saying that if Adam Smith"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 668828.0,
      "end_time": 671668.0,
      "text": "had framed out a theory of the flea market"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 671668.0,
      "end_time": 674979.0,
      "text": "instead of the free market, what would be some"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 674979.0,
      "end_time": 676988.0,
      "text": "of the principles?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 676988.0,
      "end_time": 680748.0,
      "text": "First, it would be to understand that it could be"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 680748.0,
      "end_time": 682939.0,
      "text": "considered a cooperative, and this is a thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 682939.0,
      "end_time": 687524.0,
      "text": "from the Brazilian legal scholar Roberto Mangabeira Unger."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 687524.0,
      "end_time": 690117.0,
      "text": "Cooperative development is a way forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 690117.0,
      "end_time": 694795.0,
      "text": "Secondly, from the [Austrian] anarchist philosopher Paul Feyerabend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 694795.0,
      "end_time": 699830.0,
      "text": "facts are relative, and what is a massive right"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 699830.0,
      "end_time": 702680.0,
      "text": "of self-reliance to a Nigerian businessperson"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 702680.0,
      "end_time": 706790.0,
      "text": "is considered unauthorized and horrible to other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 706790.0,
      "end_time": 708960.0,
      "text": "and we have to recognize that there are differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 708960.0,
      "end_time": 710153.0,
      "text": "in how people define things and what their facts are."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 710153.0,
      "end_time": 713253.0,
      "text": "And third is, and I&#39;m taking this from"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 713253.0,
      "end_time": 716533.0,
      "text": "the great American beat poet Allen Ginsberg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 716533.0,
      "end_time": 719685.0,
      "text": "that alternate economies barter and"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 719685.0,
      "end_time": 722435.0,
      "text": "different kinds of currency, alternate currencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 722436.0,
      "end_time": 725278.0,
      "text": "are also very important, and he talked about"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 725278.0,
      "end_time": 728269.0,
      "text": "buying what he needed just with his good looks."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 728269.0,
      "end_time": 731900.0,
      "text": "And so I just want to leave you there, and say that"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 731900.0,
      "end_time": 736116.0,
      "text": "this economy is a tremendous force for global development"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 736116.0,
      "end_time": 738830.0,
      "text": "and we need to think about it that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 738830.0,
      "end_time": 741980.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 741990.0,
      "end_time": 744224.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}